[30;1m9616 | [0m[35m       considering interactions between rows and columns children nodes.  This[0m
[30;1m9617 | [0m[35m       operation is performed recursively.  At each step, we compute axis aligned[0m
[30;1m9618 | [0m[35m       bounding boxes rows_bbox and cols_bbox: if[0m

[30;1m9620 | [0m[35m       then we consider that interaction between rows and columns degrees of[0m

[30;1m7262 | [0m[35m        \min{\gamma} \norm{\Phi^{-1}(\hat{F}_n(x_i)) - (a_1 \log(x_i - \gamma) + a_0)}_2^2[0m

[30;1m6285 | [0m[35m      If the p-value is close to zero, then we can reject this hypothesis:[0m
[30;1m6286 | [0m[35m      there is at least one nonzero coefficient.[0m
[30;1m6287 | [0m[35m    - The normality test checks that the residuals have a normal distribution.[0m
[30;1m6288 | [0m[35m      The normality assumption can be accepted (or, more precisely, cannot be[0m
[30;1m6289 | [0m[35m      rejected) if the p-value is larger than a threshold (e.g. 0.05).[0m

[31m--[ [0m[34mMatch #[0m[33m1346[0m[34m of [0m[33m2363[0m[31m ]--[0m

[30;1m318 | [0m[35m    The EGO algorithm [jones1998]_ is an adaptative optimization method based on[0m
[30;1m319 | [0m[35m    kriging.[0m
[30;1m320 | [0m[35m    An initial design of experiment is used to build a first metamodel.[0m
[30;1m321 | [0m[35m    At each iteration a new point that maximizes a criterion is chosen as[0m
[30;1m322 | [0m[35m    optimizer candidate.[0m
[30;1m323 | [0m[35m    The criterion uses a tradeoff between the metamodel value and the conditional[0m
[30;1m324 | [0m[35m    variance.[0m
